## Description : 

PDF Squeezer reduces the file size of large PDF documents.

It comes with compression capabilities which reduce the size of large PDF documents by compressing images and removing irrelevant information. This will help you obtain important savings in bandwidth costs, digital storage costs and network transmission times.

# simply drag and drop your PDF onto the application window or app icon
